[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それから私たちは、果ての大陸で見つけたマナを\n　船に積み、ランターナへの帰路につきました）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00789",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（暗黒の氷海は、行きと同じく\n　私たちに牙をむきましたが――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00790",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "絶対に全員で生きて帰るぞ！\nお前ら、気合入れろぉ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00791",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "用意周到アルビちゃん！　陽動の道具、\nちゃーんと帰りの分も持って来てるんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00792",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "コルテス",
		"romanized_name": "Kortes",
		"model_path_hash": "6745194160365014115",
		"text": "全速前進！\nお前ら、振り落とされるなよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_115_038_00793",
		"still_path_hash": "3797902451650633333",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちは誰一人欠けることなく、\n　無事に帰ることができました）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00794",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "見えてきたね、ランターナ！\nもう目とハンマーの先だよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00795",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "やっとね……！\n果ての大陸から、天才の凱旋よ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00796",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "船を降りたら、まずはオルペウス殿下へ報告だね。\nその後は――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00797",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ランターナ国民Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "錬金術士の船が、帰ってきたぞー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_728_038_00798",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "え？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00799",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ランターナ国民Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おかえりなさーい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_729_038_00800",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ランターナ国民Ｃ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "果ての大陸は、見つかったー？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_730_038_00801",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "皆さん、無事ですかー！？\n変てこ仮面さーん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_038_00802",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "こ、これは……！\n先輩方！　クリセルダさんたちも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00803",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "エルスさんに、タイニーも！\nみんな、お仕事は！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00804",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私たちが今日帰ってくるなんて、知らないわよね！？\nみんな、どうして……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00805",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "きっとみんな、待っていてくれたんだよ。\nほら、胸を張って！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00806",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "理由はなんにせよ、\nまずは、集まってくれたみんなに挨拶だ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00807",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "皆さん、お出迎えありがとうございます……！\nこんなにもたくさんの方が……！　恐悦至極です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00808",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "何を謙遜しているんだ。ランターナの民から、\nお前たちの評判はたくさん聞いたぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_038_00809",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "レスナさんがこれまで、錬金術で成し遂げてきたことが\n繋がり……今、大きな期待となっているのを感じます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_038_00810",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ランターナ国民Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "錬金術が復興すれば、これまで不可能だったことが\n可能になるかもしれない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_728_038_00811",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あなたが、ジェロンや弟くんを救ったように",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00812",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "頂獣による悲劇だって、\nなくせるかもしれない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00813",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん……！　錬金術の力があれば、きっと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00814",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "皆さん、聞いてください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00815",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "私たちは……果ての大陸へたどり着きました。\nそして、豊富なマナ資源を確認しました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00816",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "――錬金術は、復興します！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00817",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "聴衆",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ワー！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_731_038_00818_00",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "みんな、すっごい喜んでる！\nやったね、レスナちゃん！　おめでとう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00819",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うんっ！　本当に……とっても嬉しい！\nありがとう、イザナちゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00820",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "レスナ、ランターナの王子として、\n改めて感謝するよ。本当にありがとう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00821",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "こちらこそありがとうございます。\nロマンさんも、おめでとうございます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00822",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "さあ、これからが忙しいよ、錬金術士レスナ。\nこれではまだ真の復興とは言えないからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00823",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "錬金術を使った計画がたくさんあるんだ！\n国のために、同志の力を貸してほしい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00824",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もちろんです、お手伝いさせてください！\nたくさんの人を錬金術で幸せにしたいですから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00825",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "ありがとう！\nレスナならそう言ってくれると思っていたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00826",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "改めて、錬金術士レスナ。\nよろしく頼む",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_127_038_00827",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はい！　よろしくお願いいたします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00828",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "レスナ！　ロロナたちが「おめでとうパーティー」を\n開いてくれるって！　ごちそうよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00829",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ここにいないみんなも集まるって！\n行こ、レスナ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00830",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ふふっ。ありがとうございます、皆さん！\nでも、まずはオルペウス殿下に報告してからだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00831",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（師匠――見ていますか）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00832",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（再び、始まりそうです）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00833",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（錬金術の時代が……！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00834",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]